This event counts architecturally executed SVE arithmetic operation. See FP_SCALE_OPS_SPEC of ARMv9 Reference Manual for more information. This event counter is incremented by (128 / CSIZE) and by twice that amount for operations that would also be counted by SVE_FP_FMA_SPEC.

This event counts architecturally executed v8SIMD&FP arithmetic operation. See FP_FIXED_OPS_SPEC of ARMv9 Reference Manual for more information. This event counter is incremented by the specified number of elements for Advanced SIMD operations or by 1 for scalar operations, and by twice those amounts for operations that would also be counted by FP_FMA_SPEC.
